OL,4,CVatican laws changed to toughen sexual
OL,5,Cabuse punishment
OL,6, Pope Francis has changed the Roman
OL,7, Catholic Church's laws to explicitly
OL,8, criminalise sexual abuse.
OL,10,FIt is the biggest overhaul of the
OL,11,Fcriminal code for nearly 40 years.
OL,13,FThe new rules make sexual abuse,
OL,14,Fgrooming minors for sex, possessing
OL,15,Fchild pornography and covering up abuse
OL,16,Fa criminal offence under Vatican law.
OL,18,FThe Pope said one aim was to "reduce
OL,19,Fthe number of cases in which the...
OL,20,Fpenalty was left to the discretion of
OL,21,Fauthorities".
